hod je porastená hustými trnkami.Mňam\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/td\u003E\u003C\/tr\u003E\n\u003C\/tbody\u003E\u003C\/table\u003E\n\u003Cbr \/\u003E\n\u003Ctable align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEjIpstTIaSOCA0-RhWybYtA_aM4hT36k8-x5CZ2UC8g3gHhacE_7YM8lDYib1R9cLJi2RnVEmRsfUyc_lmA8GlxiaQXbV5XTGLM4zWVum3oop2VT2ktnC_sTBk7jLbj1QWrropnJWK2mjc\/s1600\/+Nerovnosti+na+ploche+hradiska.+.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\u003E\u003Cimg border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEjIpstTIaSOCA0-RhWybYtA_aM4hT36k8-x5CZ2UC8g3gHhacE_7YM8lDYib1R9cLJi2RnVEmRsfUyc_lmA8GlxiaQXbV5XTGLM4zWVum3oop2VT2ktnC_sTBk7jLbj1QWrropnJWK2mjc\/s1600\/+Nerovnosti+na+ploche+hradiska.+.jpg\" width=\"320\" \/\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/td\u003E\u003C\/tr\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003E\u0026nbsp;Nerovnosti na ploche hradiska.\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/td\u003E\u003C\/tr\u003E\n\u003C\/tbody\u003E\u003C\/table\u003E\n\u003Ctable align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEgAl8ADtN7gmM5BVEabgCEewH1oG-ZqxDhU0Ihwk1gLQil5TfkQlEFZO4yoTdeg9OB0cGLtdp08QT1yDBfvp3-mO8WNvt6NK9dSp65Hv5eUsZwgF7yIDJUm0TqV2fRcdrK8gCe29FJZgBQ\/s1600\/+Pohl%CC%8Cad+spod+za%CC%81pane%CC%81ho+valu+na+vrchol+valu.Vy%CC%81s%CC%8Cka+koli%CC%81s%CC%8Ce+od+1,5metra+do+2metrov,podl%CC%8Ca+nerovnosti%CC%81.+.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: a